# Local Workflow — CLI Commands

> **Visual flow diagrams:** [Local Dev Flow](dx-dev-local-flow.md) | [Automation Flow](dx-automation-flow.md) — mermaid diagrams showing the complete pipeline end-to-end.

All commands run in Claude Code (terminal) or as `@Agent` in VS Code Copilot chat.

## Quick Start

```
/dx-req-all <ID>    # Fetch ADO story, explain, research codebase
/dx-plan            # Generate step-by-step implementation plan
/dx-step-all        # Execute all steps (test + review + commit loop)
/dx-step-build      # Build & deploy
/dx-step-verify     # 6-phase verification
/dx-pr              # Create pull request
```

## All Commands

### Requirements

| Command | What it does | Output |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| `/dx-req-all <ID>` | Full pipeline: fetch, dor, explain, research, share approach | All spec files + ADO comments |
| `/dx-req-fetch <ID>` | Pull ADO work item, save faithfully | `raw-story.md` |
| `/dx-req-dor` | Validate DoR, post interactive checkboxes to ADO. On re-run, reads checkbox state — if BA checked items, re-validates. | `dor-report.md` + ADO comment |
| `/dx-req-explain` | Distill story into developer-focused requirements | `explain.md` |
| `/dx-req-research` | Search codebase for related code via parallel agents | `research.md` |
| `/dx-req-share` | Generate non-technical approach summary, post to ADO (idempotent) | `share-plan.md` + ADO comment |
| `/dx-req-dod` | Validate Definition of Done — tests, PR, docs, build | `dod.md` |
| `/dx-req-dod-fix` | Auto-fix failed DoD criteria, create Task WIs for the rest | Fixes + ADO tasks |
| `/dx-req-tasks <ID>` | Create child Task work items with hour estimates | ADO tasks |
| `/dx-estimate <ID>` | Estimate story complexity and effort | Estimate output |

