## Output Structure

All per-ticket output goes to `.ai/specs/<id>-<slug>/`:

```
.ai/specs/2440808-enhance-email-verification/
├── raw-story.md     # Faithful ADO dump
├── explain.md       # Developer-focused requirements
├── research.md      # Codebase research findings
├── implement.md     # Step-by-step plan with status tracking
├── share-plan.md    # Non-technical summary for Teams/ADO
├── dor-report.md    # DoR scorecard + open questions (checkbox loop with BA via ADO)
└── dod.md           # Definition of Done validation report
```
